<object-stream>
 <cz.cuni.mff.xrg.uv.transformer.sparql.construct.SparqlConstructConfig__V1>
   <query>prefix tuhat: <http://data.hulib.helsinki.fi/tuhat/>
CONSTRUCT { ?subject <http://data.hulib.helsinki.fi/attx/urn> ?urn }
WHERE {
 ?subject tuhat:link ?object .
 filter(strstarts(str(?object), 'http://urn.fi/'))
 bind(uri(strafter(str(?object), 'http://urn.fi/')) as ?urn)
}</query>
   <perGraph>true</perGraph>
 </cz.cuni.mff.xrg.uv.transformer.sparql.construct.SparqlConstructConfig__V1>
</object-stream>
